room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Excape Games in Detroit
room_description: Your group has been falsely arrested for a bank robbery and is being held at the local jail. There’s definitely something strange going on in the Sherriff’s department. You have one hour to find a way out of jail, and find the real criminals behind the robbery. You will need to work together as if your freedom depended on it because it just might.
